&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation-and-utilities&quot;&gt;Rotation and Utilities&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure skill 1 on both shroud and daggers are set to autocast. You don&#x27;t have to complete your auto-attack chain, the damage is negligible and prioritising the chain on top of other skills will lead to a DPS drop.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;rotation&quot;&gt;Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
